"      Patient information: Henoch-Sch&ouml;nlein purpura (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?10/30/10722?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Optic neuritis (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?8/59/9138?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Polyarteritis nodosa (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
