"      Patient information: Rheumatoid arthritis symptoms and diagnosis (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?28/35/29238?source=see_link\">",
